# CODEOWNERS — Automatically assigns reviewers to PRs
# See: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners
#
# Each line is a file pattern followed by one or more GitHub usernames or team names.
# The LAST matching pattern takes precedence.
#
# Update these with actual GitHub usernames / team names as the society grows.

# Default — Principal Software Engineer reviews everything not covered below
*                           @your-username

# Flight computer firmware
/flight-computer/           @your-username @flight-software-team

# Ground station
/ground-station/            @your-username @ground-station-team

# Simulations & data analysis
/simulations/               @your-username

# Shared protocol definitions — changes here affect multiple subsystems
/shared/                    @your-username

# Documentation & workshops
/docs/                      @your-username
/workshops/                 @your-username

# CI/CD and repo config — only leads should change these
/.github/                   @your-username
